Usage
	mpckbd </dev/input/eventN

Notes
	Requires Linux 'evdev' module:
		Device Drivers -> Input Device Support -> Event interface.

	Edit Makefile to set the keys used (see /usr/include/linux/input.h).
	Defaults to Power/Sleep/WakeUp for Prev/Toggle/Next.
